  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThe dialog doesn't look correct when bio has many new lines.\r\n\r\n[Kazam_screencast_00063.webm](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20650004/196141705-1644d747-ea99-4416-8e65-dc2315ae816f.webm)\r\n\r\nAdditionally profile edit form doesn't behave properly when vertically long bio is set:\r\n\r\n[Kazam_screencast_00064.webm](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20650004/196141723-386402ab-f4a6-490f-8fb3-31a69cfe9b32.webm)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nSet bio with many new lines\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nBio text should have maximum height, when more space is required it should be scrollable.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nthe whole modal content is very long\r\n\r\n",
