    "body": "@mprakhov I've worked up a few design options which I will review with the team today. There are a few related considerations that need to be resolved at the same time:\r\n\r\nOn the authoring side (here)\r\n- Do we allow carriage returns\r\n- If yes, do we expand the bio input as the user fills it\r\n- Do we have a max height for the bio input \r\n- If using a max height for the bio input we need to consider implementing a nested scrollbar for that input so the user can review their bio before saving\r\n\r\nOn the user side (someone visiting the profile card)\r\n- How do we present bios with extensive carriage returns\r\n- Do we truncate/crop the bio and have an expand / collapse function for people to view the full bio OR\r\n- Do we show the bio in full \r\n\r\nI'll come back to you later today either with recommendations from the design team or confirmation that we require sign off from John ",
